data.description: POPULAR ST. MAARTEN MODEL . . . This original owner home is being offered for sale for the first time.  Lovingly maintained, on a quiet cul-de-sac, this beautiful and popular floor plan offers 2 bedrooms, den/office/3rd bedroom and 2 bathrooms.  Neutral tile flooring throughout the home.  Kitchen has  Corian countertops and island bar seating which overlooks your spacious great room.  Sliding door has been replaced with a lovely French Door which opens to a tranquil backyard oasis of green grass and mature lime, orange and grapefruit trees.  $6000 in  irrigation system was installed in the front/back yards in 2022.  Shutter Window coverings are throughout the entire home.  The Primary Bedroom is large with ''bay bump out'' window overlooking the lush greenery.  A barn door separates the bedroom and bathroom and offers extra privacy.  Primary Bathroom has large, remodeled walk in shower, double vanity and upgraded walk in closet organizer.  Indoor Laundry Room has direct garage access.  Make this beautiful residence your own in the nationally renowned active adult community of Sun City Palm Desert. We offer 2 golf courses, lush lakes and waterfalls, pools, fitness centers, tennis, pickle and bocce ball courts, 3 clubhouses, billiard room, ballroom, restaurants, our own post office and some of the lowest HOA dues in the desert.  Come see why Money Magazine voted us 'One of the 8 greatest places to retire in America!'  Hurry this beautiful home won't last!
